[
    {
        "source_sentence": "2父子合集經卷第十七",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c21_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "西天譯經三藏朝散大夫",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c23_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "試鴻臚卿宣梵大師賜紫",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c24_0",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "沙門臣日稱等奉　詔譯六界差別品第二十六之二佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c27_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c27_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人於睡夢中，聞妙樂聲，心生適悅。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c28_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶念夢中美妙音樂，是實有不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王曰：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0966c29_23",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，是智者不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a01_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王曰：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a01_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "世尊！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a01_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a02_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "夢中畢竟無有樂聲，何況復有生適悅耶？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a02_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知是人徒自疲勞，都無有實。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a03_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a03_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a03_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a04_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚夫異生聞可意聲起於愛樂，而生染著，造作惡行，身三、語四、意業三種，作是業已剎那滅謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a06_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業滅已，不依東方南西北方四維上下中間而住，最後邊際命根滅時，自分業報皆悉現前，猶如夢覺念夢中事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a08_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a08_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因初識生起，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a11_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已，各受其報，同分心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a12_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a13_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a13_15",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a14_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "性生滅故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a14_6",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a14_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時無所從來，滅無所去；",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a15_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼業生時無所從來，滅無所去；",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a15_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生時無所從來，滅無所去。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a16_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a16_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性離故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a16_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知身識身識空，自業自業空，初識初識空，若滅滅空，若生生空，了知業轉無有作者，亦無受者，但唯名相分別顯示。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a19_12",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a20_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耳聞惡聲則生憂惱，如人夢中親愛別離，悲號啼哭，生大苦惱。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a21_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a21_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已憶夢中事，是實有不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a22_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王曰：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a22_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a22_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a22_21",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967a22_25",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
