        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b12_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b13_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "耳聞捨聲起於捨想，如人夢中聞他宣說不了義句。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967b14_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
