        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c07_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "當知諸根如幻境界如夢，一切諸法皆悉空寂，此名空解脫門；",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c08_10",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "空無空相，名無相解脫門；",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c09_2",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "若無有相，則無願求，名無願解脫門。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c09_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是三法與空共行，涅盤先道決定，如法界周遍虛空際，於此譬喻當如是知。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c11_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c12_3",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "譬如有人於睡夢中，以旃檀香或多摩羅葉香及餘香等而以塗身。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c13_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "於意云何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c13_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人覺已，憶念夢中所塗之香，是實有不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c14_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」王曰：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c14_20",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「不也！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c15_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "」佛言：",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c15_5",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c15_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是人所夢執以為實，為智者不？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c15_23",
