    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "「大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c18_11",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是，如是！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c18_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "愚夫異生初聞妙香便生愛樂，心起染著，造如是業，身三、語四、意三種業，造彼業已，即便滅謝。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c20_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "是業滅已，不依四方四維上下中間而住，乃至最後識滅，自業現前，猶如夢覺念夢中事。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c22_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c22_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "識為其主，業為攀緣，二種相因，初識生起，或趣地獄，或墮傍生、琰摩羅界及阿脩羅，若人若天。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c25_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生已，各受其報，同分心品相續隨轉，最後識滅名為死蘊，最初識起名為生蘊。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c26_17",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c27_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "無有少法從於此世得至他世。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c27_14",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "所以者何？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c27_19",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "性生滅故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c28_4",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "大王！",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c28_7",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "身識生時無所從來，滅無所去；",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c29_1",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "彼業生時，無所從來，滅無所去；",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0967c29_16",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "初識生時，無所從來，滅無所去。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968a01_9",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "何以故？",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968a01_13",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "自性離故。",
        "from": "T11n0320_017:0968a01_18",
        "context_with_next_sentence": true
    },
    {
        "source_sentence": "如是了知身識身識空，自業自業空，初識初識空，若滅滅空，若生生空。",
